得熟，時時刻刻能提得起，這端身正念。<br />\n南無阿彌陀佛🙇&zwj;♀️🙇&zwj;♀️🙇&zwj;♀️ </span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n🙏祈願師父上淨下空老和尚。法體安康。正法久住。度生無量。南無阿彌陀佛！<br />\n<br />\n🙇&zwj;♀️隨喜功德分享此文。皆悉回向給文章、圖片原作者(佛友大德)和眾讀者(佛友大德)及盡虛空遍法界一切眾生。<br />\n<br />\n📢感恩南無阿彌陀佛。閱讀開智慧。分享好文。利人利己。正法流通。功德無量。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-18T11:03:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BDmkTvD.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBDmkTvD.png&h=ae595847&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f7543f3850570639ba954b8b0815835c80fb29c2","tid":2069409,"uid":347001,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"4ff24d5132cd4cc77c818f8450e3752aab6e5d3f","tid":2069409,"uid":347001,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":7,"replyTime":"2020-06-18T11:02:02.000Z","msg":"念念不忘阿彌陀佛<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">學佛就是將佛陀的教誨落實到日常生活當中</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n與佛有緣的同修可以在Facebook search 淨空法師/阿彌陀佛/念佛成佛 搜索更多經文+智慧字句<br />\n許多佛菩薩都把經文的精華/重點節錄了出來<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/groups/amituofobuddha/?ref=share\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fgroups%2Famituofobuddha%2F%3Fref%3Dshare&d=j4yDeGq49jMu68ZzGhcJHnqIiw1YZhwEtH0I4AgSOk0%3D&h=760c32fa\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/groups/amituofobuddha/?ref=share</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/nianAmitabha/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FnianAmitabha%2F&d=j4yDeGq49jMu68ZzGhcJHnqIiw1YZhwEtH0I4AgSOk0%3D&h=c6cb9403\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/nianAmitabha/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/kanpofanxia/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fkanpofanxia%2F&d=j4yDeGq49jMu68ZzGhcJHnqIiw1YZhwEtH0I4AgSOk0%3D&h=227bc74e\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/kanpofanxia/</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;